    public class ProbabilityBasedQueueDispatchingPolicy
extends ObjectSequencePolicy<UserQueue>
    Defines a dispatching policy for multi-queue structure. The policy is based on a probability distribution that specified the probability for the dispatching of a user towards each queue.
